{"tid":573153,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"S845 打孖來！數 8 個愛與恨 Sony Xperia XZ2 6GB 旗艦登場","createTime":"2018-02-26T07:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T05:58:40.000Z","uid":731,"like":7,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e1fdc19ed6782808a92c045964f1059a16cf56","tid":573153,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:52:12.000Z","msg":"今年Sony嘅機....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高規 001 ：用最高檔 S845 CPU<br />\nSony Xperia XZ2 是今年首批採用高通 Snapdragon 845 處理器的 Android手機，支援 4G+4G 雙卡雙待的功能，SIM 卡槽同樣是三選二的 Combo 式設計，XZ2 也是 Sony Mobile 首款內建 6GB RAM 的機種，並有 64GB 儲存空間。<br />\n<br />\n驚喜 002：又係玩水嘅 Ambient Flow 設計概念<br />\n改款了，改款了，Sony 手機終於改款了！Sony Xperia XZ2 係外觀設計上，不再 Omni Balance，都唔玩 Loop Surface ，大家唔記得係乜唔緊要，今日起記多一個 Term：Ambient Flow。今次 Sony 為 Xperia XZ2 帶來全新設計「Ambient Flow」。Sony 說 Ambient Flow 即是「液體的表面張力弧線」，令 Xperia XZ2 一改過去方方正正的外表，手機在弧度的呈現上比起不久前發表的 Xperia XA2 系列更加強烈，同時正面與背面都是採用 Gorilla Glass 5 玻璃材質的設計，讓原本方方正正的手機外型，變得更加圓滑。呢個 Ambient Flow 設計，帶來兩個好處，首先是 Xperia XZ2 都會支援 IP65/68 防水防塵，另外就是造到支援 Qi 無線充電。新外型，保留 Sony 手機嘅強項，加入更受歡迎嘅功能，係唔錯嘅！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4551/210200/1/rv/sony-xperia-xz2-launch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4551%2F210200%2F1%2Frv%2Fsony-xperia-xz2-launch%2F&d=4dFubs1SaL5s%2BWI6%2Fcp11ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cbd6c399\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4551/210200/1/rv/sony-xperia-xz2-launch/</a>"},{"pid":"0144e1e3eebb86e0f407534e9d04fbc19a7b36f3","tid":573153,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:10:27.000Z","msg":"點解mon ratio仲係做到咁低架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a2df199eae82e73ac2a6cbdbd140fa944ab672","tid":573153,"uid":141060,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"連唯一優勢　型<br />\n<br />\n都無乜撚埋"},{"pid":"17b574a2ffd25df756f17622083a6813bd12a1cf","tid":573153,"uid":